# 🌐 4️⃣ Cloud Storage vs Database

A common interview topic.

---

## Cloud Storage

Stores files:

* images
* videos
* PDFs

---

### Examples

* User profile photos
* Uploaded resumes
* YouTube videos

---

### Mental Model

Digital warehouse 📦

---

## Database

Stores structured data:

* user details
* orders
* messages

---

### Example

```text
User:
Name
Email
Phone
```

---

### Mental Model

Digital spreadsheet 📊

---

### Quick Comparison

| Storage | Database        |
| ------- | --------------- |
| Files   | Structured data |
| Images  | User records    |
| Videos  | Transactions    |

